MALE PALP (
<figureCitation box="[375,453,305,332]" captionStart="Fig. 7" captionStartId="11.[227,270,2002,2028]" captionTargetBox="[313,1322,1192,1988]" captionTargetId="figure@11.[295,1353,1166,1996]" captionTargetPageId="11" captionText="Fig. 7. Ballomma haddadi gen. et sp. nov. A – B. Holotype, ♂. C. ♀ (MRAC 132641). A. Male palp, retrolateral view. B. As preceding, ventral view. C. Epigyne, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1406686/files/figure.png" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Figs 7</figureCitation>
<collectionCode box="[453,474,305,331]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">A</collectionCode>
