<paragraph blockId="13.[227,1437,406,502]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">
COLOUR. Carapace (
<figureCitation box="[462,534,406,433]" captionStart="Fig. 6" captionStartId="10.[227,270,1966,1992]" captionTargetBox="[245,1418,755,1933]" captionTargetId="figure@10.[245,1418,755,1934]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="Fig. 6. Ballomma haddadi gen. et sp. nov. A – B. Holotype, ♂. C – F. ♀ (MRAC 132641). A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. As preceding, ventral view. C. Habitus, dorsal view. D. As preceding, ventral view. E. Prosoma, frontal view. F. Prosoma, dorsolateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3471690" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3471690/files/figure.png" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Fig. 6</figureCitation>
<collectionCode box="[534,553,406,433]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">C</collectionCode>
– 
<collectionCode box="[569,586,406,433]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">F</collectionCode>
